    "date": "2022-03-28T15:53:34Z",
    "text": "National Commission on the COVID-19 Pandemic Act\n\nThis bill temporarily establishes the National Commission on the COVID-19 Pandemic in the legislative branch to investigate the facts and circumstances regarding the emergence of, spread of, and response to COVID-19. The commission terminates 90 days after it submits a final report of its findings and recommendations."
